with all sector-specific requirements applicable to the Licensee. The Licensor
gently reminds the Licensee that the prohibition on Production use in Article
III should substantially mitigate any sector-specific regulatory concerns,
inasmuch as regulatory authorities are generally not concerned with software
that is not deployed in Production.

Section 17.04. SEVERABILITY OF THIS ARTICLE. This Article XVII is included for
the purpose of addressing regulatory and governmental considerations. The
